						<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Fragmentation (computing)</span></h1>
						<div id="bodyContent">
								<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub">  (Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Fragmentation_(computer)&amp;redirect=no" title="Fragmentation (computer)">Fragmentation (computer)</a>)</div>
